      <title>斯洛文尼亚计划发行欧盟首只主权可持续发展相关债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/slovenia-plans-first-sovereign-sustainability-linked-bond-in-eu</link>
