      <title>通胀放缓提振美联储降息预期 美国国债价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/treasuries-surge-as-easing-inflation-boosts-fed-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于温和的通胀数据促使交易员恢复押注美联储将在7月前再次降息，美国国债价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/treasuries-surge-as-easing-inflation-boosts-fed-rate-cut-bets</guid>
